      "content": "wait, \"rookie mistake\"? lol. i just don't like being on these meds if i don't need them. my stomach has been feeling kinda weird and nauseous since i started the pills. if the skin is already healed, isn't it better to just avoid the unnecessary side effects and extra chemicals? if i stop now, am i really going to be in danger?",
